data.description: This home shows its character from 1901 but also has many current updates. Conveniently located in the Thompson square this 122 year old home features 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, large kitchen, dining room, living room, walk out basement, and detached barn/garage.  Updates include: New roof (2019), all new flooring (2022), new siding (2022), new furnace (2021) and new kitchen (20021).
